#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "thag1.41:4.1"
msgid "1.41. Sirivaḍḍhattheragāthā"
msgstr "1.41. Sirivaḍḍha"

#. </h1></div><blockquote class="gatha"><p><a class="sc" id="1"></a><a
#. class="vns" id="vns41"></a><a class="vnp" id="vnp41"></a>
msgctxt "thag1.41:5.1"
msgid "“Vivaramanupatanti vijjutā,"
msgstr "Lightning flashes down"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag1.41:5.2"
msgid "Vebhārassa ca paṇḍavassa ca;"
msgstr "on the cleft of Vebhāra and Paṇḍava."

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag1.41:5.3"
msgid "Nagavivaragato ca jhāyati,"
msgstr "But in the mountain cleft he is absorbed in jhāna—"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag1.41:5.4"
msgid "Putto appaṭimassa tādino”ti."
msgstr "the son of the Buddha, inimitable and poised."

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
